parameters:
\nw[\N[21]]It's getting dark soon... Should I rest here
today?

\nw[\N[21]](I had a bad feeling about this... but there's no
point in worrying. Let's just talk to the coachman
and start our journey.)

\nw[Coachman]Wow, that was impressive. Please continue to do
your best starting from tomorrow.

\nw[Uka]It's hot... I don't like it... It's warm... I like
it...

\nw[Thorz]The magic consumption is just too intense. I'll
have to replenish it.

\nw[Thorz]Since she's an elf, she must have high magic
resistance... I wonder what I should do...

\nw[Huma]Incubi and succubi can restore their magical power
and physical strength through sexual activity~.
Let's do it together to relieve fatigue~.

\nw[Fross]I don't have much experience with camping. Even
during the war, I was in an area with minimal
damage.

\nw[\N[21]]I was born in Dios, you know. I've heard that this
country was in a terrible condition, but Dios
never invaded us.

\nw[Fross]Yes... After the birth of the Misura Kingdom, Dios
invaded us, causing quite a bit of damage.

\nw[\N[21]]I know that. My parents were soldiers too. They
said they advanced about one-third of the way from
the border to the center.

\nw[\N[21]]But in the end, we were defeated by the two Aegis.
No.I Marshal, the hero who excelled in the war,
and No.IX Eater, the giant who seemed invincible.

\nw[Fross]But it's true that the villages and towns along
that route were in a terrible state. There was
already civil unrest and war, and food was scarce,
but then they were plundered by the Dios army.

\nw[Fross]If it becomes known that Dios is your hometown,
there might be people who hold a grudge. Please be
careful.
\nw[\N[21]]Um, that's not what I wanted to talk about.

\nw[\N[21]]Fross, please have sex with me until we reach our
destination.

\nw[\N[21]]There are two reasons. First, we will use magic
orbs to ward off monsters ahead.

\nw[Fross]I've heard that magic orbs don't have much effect
in warding off monsters...

\nw[\N[21]]Well, it's just a little difficult to come by. It
wouldn't make much sense to use it within our
territory, but if we use it in an area where
monsters don't inhabit, it will become less likely
for them to approach.

\nw[\N[21]]We've passed through the area where many monsters
appear. From tomorrow, we can expect a high
effect.

\nw[\N[21]]Maintaining this barrier requires a considerable
amount of magical power. That's why we need to
generate magical power.
\nw[Fross]I see... What is the other reason?

\nw[\N[21]]It's to send magical power to Prae. I'm the one
who made a contract with Prae. Compared to the two
familiars, I can directly obtain magical power
through the abilities of an incubus, so the amount
of magical power sent to Prae will be greater.

\nw[Fross]......I understand the reasons. But I can't really
separate myself from everyone like that, and we
can't be alone together, right?

\nw[\N[21]]Just give up on that. To be honest, even I feel
embarrassed.

\nw[\N[21]]You must be tired from walking today. Starting
tomorrow, Fross will be traveling by carriage, so
I'll rely on you from tomorrow.

\nw[Fross]............I understand. It's very embarrassing,
but it's my request, after all.

\nw[\N[21]]Thank goodness. Since you're helping me, the
request fee will be reduced.

\nw[\N[21]]You must be tired from today, so please rest and
take it easy.

\nw[\N[21]](It seems like it will take some time after all...
I hope \N[1] will be okay...)
\nw[Coachman]Please let me know when we're departing.

\nw[Uka]......Ants?......I don't really...have any
thoughts about them?
\nw[\N[3]]Even if you come at me so forcefully...

\nw[Huma]We still have time before departure, so just the
tip is fine!
\nw[\N[21]]It's not a good idea to move from here.
\nw[\N[21]]It's not a good idea to move from here.

There's no point in going any further from here.
Let's turn back.
\nw[\N[21]]It's not a good idea to move from here.
\nw[\N[21]]It's not a good idea to move from here.
